text.tspan: During the usability tests, when users clicked on “Invite Friends”, they were explicitly confused as the prototype directly took them
to the platform they shared to such as WhatsApp, with no screen transition. A user said, “Am I still on Time Out?”
To eliminate the feeling that they are lost in the process and confusion, we added a transition message which says “Awesome, you
are now being redirected to WhatsApp” to give them a cue that they are being redirected to another platform.
